snippet.title: Memoranda - Nintendo Switch Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Memoranda is inspired by the surreal world short stories of Japanese novelist Haruki Murakami and tells the story of a young woman who gradually realizes that she is forgetting her own name. But is she really losing her memory, or is there something else that could explain the strange situation?

Coming to the Nintendo Switch in 2020.
